{"tid":1882384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家係軍火佬直播公審一事上可以分開嚟計","createTime":"2020-02-16T08:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T03:52:48.000Z","uid":88834,"like":25,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cef3e9509eae25776384a5a60a06e8bf26d658fc","tid":1882384,"uid":88834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"無可否認大部分人都覺得軍火佬利用自己記者嘅身份嚟公審人係濫用左佢嘅職能，而到依家佢係自己個page嘅態度都係唔覺自己有錯，要佢為呢樣野道歉我係絕對贊成。<br />\n<br />\n但係希望各位<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好因為咁而同一眾高登記者包括軍火佬割席！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有睇過高登直播嘅都會知佢地係反送中運動入面有幾搏，例如爆炸頭係理大之戰入面全程直擊、軍火佬為左問到被捕手足個名而企到幾咁前、被捕人士關注組入面一部分相嘅來源係高登記者提供。佢地係呢場運動所付出嘅我唔敢話比手足多，但佢地絕對係我地係運動入面嘅同路人。<br />\n<br />\n軍火佬平時係點嘅人我唔清楚，不過不割席就係不割席。指責點都會有㗎啦，我亦都因為佢咁樣公審人而失望，但係唔好因為一件事而無限放大甚至起佢底，我咁講係想為手足提供多一重嘅保障，亦係想佢會因而會改善，繼續做好真正要履行嘅職責。<br />\n<br />\n對事不對人，希望大家可以以大局為重，就算軍火佬唔道歉，佢嘅直播只要係同反送中運動有關嘅我都唔會選擇忽視，因為我欣賞並支持佢作為同路人所做嘅野。佢嘅道歉之後先問佢收返。<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁易俾人分化啦好嗎？"},{"pid":"cafd4dbe17a7238f6cc505fd5483110319c3300e","tid":1882384,"uid":194399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"(借位thx) 請各位開發新戰線 : Youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目的: 利用youtube演算法, 增加黃絲channel及文宣曝光機會, 降低藍絲文宣的散播速度, 應對中共KOL 100計劃<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲channel&rarr; like、comment、subscribe、share</span><br />\n藍絲channel&rarr; 不感興趣 /不要推薦這個頻道、開1.2秒close(降低續看率)<br />\n<ins>進一步措施</ins> : 利用家中長輩ac dislike + report藍片 &amp;<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 觀看+like黃片</span> (提高黃片在其年齡層的曝光度)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【中共最新滲透計劃 : KOL 100】    <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1881621\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1881621</a></span>"},{"pid":"e01d491210a362de3df41649356eaeff43640958","tid":1882384,"uid":88834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c9522b81e6e96629df5b45b94220b5e4cd8c9a5","tid":1882384,"uid":88834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"只要仲係同路人，就唔好割席"},{"pid":"084c51d2ee7ed2f02e323becc782a4dfd6eed3fb","tid":1882384,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"明顯係三毛國安抹黑軍火佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f8c81bd6b9be26bda8901845e7276258a277cf","tid":1882384,"uid":88834,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"084c51d2ee7ed2f02e323becc782a4dfd6eed3fb","tid":1882384,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:29:40.000Z","msg":"明顯係三毛國安抹黑軍火佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"見到有唔少巴打都係對事only，但有啲放大到要起底，分化五毛味極重"},{"pid":"8454fa2145313fc874e7da8732b2a9ff87981f98","tid":1882384,"uid":88834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T08:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc5e1bf57ac622a6d8b8cc004a966aaa58886703","tid":1882384,"uid":25168,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"佢係90年代mk格姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人係好既"},{"pid":"ec697b3ac4b73485be3ec3bcb95011b394d8d112","tid":1882384,"uid":139117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc5e1bf57ac622a6d8b8cc004a966aaa58886703","tid":1882384,"uid":25168,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"佢係90年代mk格姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人係好既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"咁佢道歉未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5d0ff10b6d0a62